description:
The Third Sunday Before Christmas Week: Episode One is narrated by the prophet, Isaiah. He explains how the prophets of the Old Testament foretold the coming of mankinds savior, Jesus, long before he was born.

Isaiah explains how God started preparing for the birth of Jesus before the world was created, and gave hints about the coming of Jesus throughout the Old Testament.

Eyewitness Bible Series is pleased to present the Christmas Series. This series is a collection of 10 new episodes designed to be watched on the three Sundays prior to Christmas week, plus the seven days of Christmas week, ending on Christmas Day.

Scripture: Isaiah 9:6, 11:1; Micah 5:2; John 1:1-3
